        <num>CC 2704</num>
        <heading>2704.  Nonpayment of rent</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2704.  Nonpayment of rent
If the lessee fails to pay the rent when due, the lessor may, in accordance with the provisions of the Title &quot;Conventional Obligations or Contracts&quot;, dissolve the lease and may regain possession in the manner provided by law.</p>
        </content>
